dct_description_sm: Translation of title: Chekiang, Tenth Imperial Province of China.
Chekiang is also known as Zhejiang Sheng.
Coloured cartouche in right hand lower corner is possibly first European illustration of silk or cotton making in China.
Plate [11] from: Novus atlas sinensis a Martino Martinus, Soc. Iesu. [Amsterdam : Joh. Blaeu, 1655].
